{
  "texts": [
    "3D models are utilized to avoid information loss that happens when 3D MRI data is transformed into 2D images for analysis by 2D convolutional filters.",
    "Data preprocessing through co-registration, skull stripping, brain masking, and re-sampling were employed.",
    "It is implemented on a system with NVIDIA RTX2080 GPU using Keras, and TensorFlow.",
    "The accuracy of the proposed model through the 5-fold cross validation techniques are 73.4% on the ADNI dataset and 69.9% on the OASIS dataset respectively.",
    "If the network shape and hyperparameters had been tuned, the classification accuracy would have increased."
  ]
}